item.title: Shilo Pa - Straight To The Heart - Ukulele Underground
item.description: Play along video for the song Straight To The Heart by Shilo Pa from the channel Ukulele Underground. Chords used in the song: Amaj7, Bm7, C♯m7, Dmaj7, E7.

item.title: Paul McCartney - Wonderful Christmas Time - Baritone Ukulele - Key of A - ukeplayalongs
item.description: Play along video for the song Wonderful Christmas Time by Paul McCartney from the channel ukeplayalongs. Chords used in the song: A, Amaj7, Bm, C♯m, D, E, E7, F♯m7, F♯m7add4, G.
